data.description: Discover your ideal family retreat nestled in the heart of Palm Coast! This two-story home is thoughtfully designed for families or those on the brink of parenthood. Upstairs, find all the bedrooms, providing a private sanctuary for rest and relaxation. Downstairs, the expansive living areas flow seamlessly together, highlighted by a spacious kitchen that begs for gatherings and culinary creations. The living room boasts stunning shiplap accents, infusing the space with coastal charm and warmth. Venture outside to the backyard, where endless potential awaits for outdoor fun and relaxation. Conveniently situated near schools, parks, and amenities, this home offers not just comfort, but also convenience, making it the perfect setting for creating lasting family memories.
